UNITED STATES ex rel. Omar Lenox MACKLEM, Relator Appellant, v. COMMISSIONER OF IMMIGRATION AT THE PORT OF NEW YORK, Respondent Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 15, 1926.) No. 263. Isaac Shorr, of New York City (Carol Weiss King, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Nathan R. Margold, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for respondent appellee.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and MANTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
